name: Felicity Jones [Embedding]
description:
Felicity Jones, requested by good ol' @lemke! Felicity Jones is an actress best known for playing in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.

It was brought to my attention that there's another model up for Felicity Jones, a LyCORIS of her by @malcolmrey . Combining it with the embedding provided on this page yields some unique results and is definitely worth experimenting with!

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. While testing the embed I noticed that on some models (such as the protogen series) there is a tendency to create grey monotone backgrounds. Strong prompting or putting the token for Koh_FelicityJones a bit more towards the end largely mends this issue.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
